"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/439366","Department for Culture, Media and Sport","false","2016-01-05","<p>A reply to the letter from the right hon member for Manchester, Gorton, was sent on 21 December.</p>","Wantage","Mr Edward Vaizey",,"2016-01-05T15:51:26.797Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/439366/answer","Biography information for Mr Edward Vaizey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/439366/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/439366/answer",,,,,"10","Culture, Media and Sport","Culture, Media and Sport","2015-12-17","Members: Correspondence","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport, when he intends to answer the letter to him from the right hon. Member for Manchester, Gorton, dated 9 November 2015 with regard to Mr S Hewitt.","false","Biography information for Sir Gerald Kaufman","Manchester, Gorton","Sir Gerald Kaufman","20691"
